What you need to know:

Spectators were barred from the departure ceremony and first leg over ongoing fears about the coronavirus, which forced the 2020 Games' historic postponement a year agoTokyo 2020 chief Seiko Hashimoto said the flame was "a ray of light at the end of the darkness"The Fukushima launch also puts the spotlight back on the northeastern region of Tohoku that was affected by the 2011 quake, tsunami and nuclear disaster